title: Sklep z goframi
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, European, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Waffle cafe behind the Copernicus statue. Makes both sweet and savory waffles, with a vegan menu section. The sweet vegan waffles can be served with jam, nuts, fresh peanut butter, roasted apples with cinnamon, vegan whipped cream. The savory vegan waffles are served either with arugula, pear, roasted sunflower seeds, balsamic sauce, or with chili sin carne.
